@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dfkyte(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((0.80 - v0))
    v2 = v2
    v2 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.04 / v0 + 0.58) * v1))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.83) * (tmp + 0.03 - v1 + 0.47)) + tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
